/// floating point arithmetics and subsequently casting the result to the desired integer value. For <see cref="F:ILNumerics.ArrayStyles.numpy" /> no such
/// precautions exist and the result of the binary operation is exactly the same as for operating the elements as System types (and as in numpy itself).</item></list></para></remarks>
