/// <see cref="P:ILNumerics.fcomplex.NaN" /> the element from <paramref name="A" /> is returned.</para><para>If <paramref name="omitNaN" /> is false the result is <see cref="P:ILNumerics.fcomplex.NaN" /> if at least
